videos.headline: Army caps off 8-minute drive with TD
videos.description: Army's long first drive of the game ends with a 1-yard touchdown run from Kelvin Hopkins Jr.

videos.headline: Hopkins eludes defenders for 77-yard TD
videos.description: Kelvin Hopkins Jr. makes multiple defenders miss on a 77-yard score for his second touchdown of the day, putting Army up 14-0.

videos.headline: Army takes fumble to house for TD
videos.description: James Nachtigal forces the Houston QB to fumble, then Cameron Jones scoops and scores to put Army up 21-0.

videos.headline: Houston gets on board with 3-yard TD pass
videos.description: QB Clayton Tune fires the ball into a tight window for Romello Brooker on the 3-yard touchdown, giving Houston its first score of the game.

videos.headline: Hopkins' 54-yard pass leads to his 3rd TD
videos.description: Kelvin Hopkins Jr. completes a 54-yard pass to Kjetil Cline, setting the QB up for his third rushing TD of the game.

videos.headline: Hopkins runs in 4th TD of game for Army
videos.description: QB Kelvin Hopkins Jr. finds the end zone for his fourth rushing touchdown of the game, putting Army up 35-7.

videos.headline: Hopkins ties 2 records with TD
videos.description: QB Kelvin Hopkins Jr. ties two Army school records with his fifth rushing touchdown of the game, which is also his 17th for the season.
